        "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
        "body": "The problem is in the fact that the `getRelativePath` method we use (from ANT) uses canonical paths. It shouldn't do that, but instead only compare the normalized paths just like all other code in Gradle. We can use `java.nio.Path.relativize` for that.",
